SUMMARY:Deadline: Unruly Mirrors Open Call 2026 (East and Central Asia\, Fe
 minist Art)
DESCRIPTION:Unruly Mirrors is an open call for artists based in Kazakhstan\
 , Japan\, South Korea\, Mainland China\, Hong Kong\, Uzbekistan\, or Mongo
 lia. The project examines beauty practices in East and Central Asia as spa
 ces of norm reproduction\, intimacy\, and feminist resistance. Financial s
 upport and full eligibility criteria were not publicly confirmed at time o
 f entry (the website was unreachable). Deadline: 15 July 2026. Apply or in
 quire at https://unrulymirrors.com. NOTE: verify financial support and ful
 l details directly before applying.\n\nOrganisation: Unruly Mirrors\nLocat
 ion: East and Central Asia (Kazakhstan\, Japan\, South Korea\, Mainland Ch
 ina\, Hong Kong\, Uzbekistan\, Mongolia)\nAward: Financial support details
  not publicly confirmed at time of entry. No application fee confirmed.\nD
 uration: Not publicly confirmed.\n\nMore: https://unrulymirrors.com?utm_so
 urce=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
URL:https://unrulymirrors.com?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_med
 ium=referral
LOCATION:East and Central Asia (Kazakhstan\, Japan\, South Korea\, Mainland
  China\, Hong Kong\, Uzbekistan\, Mongolia)
